data.description: Beautiful four-bedroom two bathroom home located in Navajo Ranch. Step back and enjoy the peace and quiet of country living while still having easy access to Hwy 160 and all the amenities of the towns of Walsenburg & La Veta just a short distance away. This home features over 1800 sqft of spacious living, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. With its beautiful mountain views, this property provides a tranquil and serene atmosphere that will leave you feeling relaxed and refreshed. Don't miss your chance to own this beautiful home – schedule a viewing today!
